45
00:01:48,100 --> 00:01:50,470
Said to be killed by a deadly poison

46
00:01:51,050 --> 00:03:39,760
The mayor under the tower

47
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:55,960
Time passed, and in the XX century

48
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:59,410
A group of scientists

49
00:01:59,410 --> 00:02:02,120
Unearthed the mayor's corpse

50
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:04,020
In order to perform an autopsy

51
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:08,560
