58
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,780
Near the clock tower

59
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:38,290
Two siblings were playing soccer together

60
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:42,790
At one point, the ball started rolling away

61
00:02:42,790 --> 00:02:44,930
Until it reached a grassy spot

62
00:02:44,930 --> 00:02:48,100
Right under the clock tower

63
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:51,170
And in that grassy spot...

64
00:02:51,570 --> 00:02:54,870
There was a man on all fours

65
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:56,870
In desperate search for something

66
00:02:57,440 --> 00:03:00,980
When the big brother hurried up to get the ball back

67
00:03:01,980 --> 00:03:03,750
The figure of that man...

68
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,850
Already disappeared

69
00:03:07,180 --> 00:03:08,720
The brother, who found it eerie,

70
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,720
Hurried up and picked the ball up

71
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,880
And quickly run back to his sister

72
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:14,860
But then, she noticed something

73
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:16,760
And shouted as if in pure agony:

74
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:19,440
"NOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!"

75
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,770
The brother, surprised,

76
00:03:26,170 --> 00:03:28,870
Looked down to the soccer ball he was holding

77
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:30,570
And then...

78
00:03:31,870 --> 00:03:33,310
He realized...

79
