174
00:08:33,990 --> 00:08:40,180
Brazil representative

175
00:08:34,780 --> 00:08:40,180
Marzia

176
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:38,480
So, our representative for Brazil is miss Marzia

177
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,850
Pleased to meet you       - Same here

178
00:08:40,850 --> 00:08:42,120
It's a pleasure

179
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,120
Whenever you're ready

180
00:08:50,250 --> 00:08:52,590
The story I'm about to tell you

181
00:08:52,590 --> 00:08:57,230
Is about an experience I really had
in Brazil when I was 14 years old

182
00:08:57,870 --> 00:09:00,000
I was still very young

183
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:03,870
And I was trying to call
for a ghost, just for fun

184
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:09,880
In short, I was doing something
like the japanese "kokkuri-san"

185
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:09,880
note: a divination game similar to the western ouija board

186
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:14,350
On the table, I've placed

187
00:09:13,080 --> 00:11:25,960
The summoned spirit

188
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:17,750
Two cards labeled with "no" and "yes"

189
00:09:18,050 --> 00:09:20,490
Then I've light up two candles

190
00:09:20,490 --> 00:09:24,330
And planned to ask the ghost some questions

191
00:09:24,330 --> 00:09:26,090
So it would answer, that's it

192
00:09:26,730 --> 00:09:29,530
And so, I started the ritual

193
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,830
But then suddenly

194
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,840
The wind started to blow

195
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,810
And when I opened my eyes

196
00:09:38,810 --> 00:09:39,870
Before me

197
00:09:41,470 --> 00:09:43,680
There was a blond kid

198
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:46,810
So I asked him

199
00:09:47,910 --> 00:09:49,950
"Who are you?"

200
00:09:51,250 --> 00:09:52,720
And he said

201
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:55,090
"I'm Paolo"

202
00:09:55,090 --> 00:09:57,660
"I died in an accident"

203
00:09:57,660 --> 00:10:01,060
"And I don't have any friends,
so why don't you play with me?"

204
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:06,600
That was the first time I saw
a real ghost right before me

205
00:10:07,990 --> 00:10:10,040
So I got really scared

206
00:10:12,140 --> 00:10:13,840
So I told Paolo

207
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:16,740
"You're not in this world anymore"

208
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:21,650
"You shouldn't be here" - I desperately told him

209
00:10:23,950 --> 00:10:25,450
And so he

210
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:29,950
Quietly pointed his index towards the "no" card

211
00:10:29,950 --> 00:10:33,830
I gradually became even more terrified

212
00:10:33,830 --> 00:10:36,130
And, scared, I told him "go home"

213
00:10:36,130 --> 00:10:38,130
"Please, just go back home!"

214
00:10:38,530 --> 00:10:40,840
And yet

215
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:44,140
He just kept on pointing the "no" card

216
00:10:45,610 --> 00:10:47,740
So i took the cards and the candles

217
00:10:47,740 --> 00:10:49,740
On the table and took them away

218
00:10:51,100 --> 00:10:52,580
And cleaned everything up

219
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:55,780
And while shutting both my eyes and ears

220
00:10:56,250 --> 00:11:00,960
"Go away! Go Away! Vá embora! Vá embora!"

221
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,560
I just kept on shouting this

222
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,590
And after some time

223
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:08,000
He disappeared into thin air

224
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,100
But...

225
00:11:12,330 --> 00:11:16,340
On the table, there was a single tarot card left

226
00:11:17,810 --> 00:11:19,970
When I looked at that tarot card...

227
00:11:20,640 --> 00:11:22,410
I realized its meaning...

228
00:11:22,990 --> 00:11:25,150
...was "friendship"

229
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:34,020
Paolo...

230
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,760
So, you actually experienced this?

231
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:39,120
I was around 14 years old      - 14 years old...

232
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:43,840
I've always been kind of sensitive to ghost sighting

233
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:46,200
They're always sticking close to me

234
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,290
And always pop out, like, a lot of them

235
00:11:48,290 --> 00:11:50,780
So there's a chance it could stick close to us?

236
00:11:50,780 --> 00:11:52,540
It could happen, yes

237
00:11:52,540 --> 00:11:53,410
Will it be Paolo?

238
00:11:53,410 --> 00:11:56,040
If you call him, he may come but---

239
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,510
Even tigers could come

240
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,180
A tiger?

241
00:11:58,180 --> 00:12:02,150
It actually happened I was once possessed by a tiger

242
00:12:03,450 --> 00:12:05,450
It's not something to laugh about!

243
00:12:05,450 --> 00:12:08,350
I'm not trying to sound funny

244
00:12:08,350 --> 00:12:10,890
This too was from that time,
I was like 15 years old

245
00:12:10,890 --> 00:12:12,060
And what happened?

246
00:12:12,060 --> 00:12:12,630
A tiger

247
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:14,200
And what happened?

248
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,660
It bit me

249
00:12:15,660 --> 00:12:17,500
It bit you?      - It did

250
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:19,330
It bit you?      - Yes, on the neck

251
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,070
It's scary, huhh

252
00:12:21,070 --> 00:12:22,000
What is it?

253
00:12:22,670 --> 00:12:25,920
But it would be scary even if it wasn't a ghost

254
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,800
No way!

255
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:30,750
I mean, even if a non-ghost tiger would bite you...

